These are Puzzles for 4x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x6-Level-2-1::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, hiking, skydiving, video-games, fishing
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, cola, mirinda, 7up, hot-chocolate
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, october, april, january, september, march
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, boat, car, helicopter, roller, taxi
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 3. the person driving the roller is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person drinking cola##2
 5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
12. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
13. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
14. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking water##1
15. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
16. the person driving the car is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Hobby          | fishing   | filmmaking     | rock-climbing | skydiving     | hiking     | video-games   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | 7up  | cola  | hot-chocolate | water | almond-milk |
| Birthday         | october | september | april | january    | december  | march |
| Transport     | boat     | helicopter    | bike    | roller   | taxi      | car    |

