 9. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
11. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of pop##1
12. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person driving the train##1
